document_data.name: Timewarp
document_data.mainbody: '''''Timewarp''''' was a powerful southern magic [[divine magic|divine]] spell available to worshipers of [[Thoth]].
document_data.Effects: When cast, this spell allowed the caster to send a single creature up to two minutes in past. The spell took a physical toll on the caster, aging their body by a full year.
document_data.Components: In addition to [[somatic]] and [[verbal]] components, this spell required a [[material component]] in the form of [[sand]].
